</emphasis>
Total length: 4.35. Carapace 1.97 long, 1.34 wide, 0.95 high. Ocular quadrangle 0.97 long. Anterior eye row 1.26 wide, posterior 1.08 wide. Legs 4312. Length of legs: I 2.98 (1.04 + 1.12 + 0.82); II 2.89 (1.05 + 1.04 + 0.80); III 3.81 (1.30 + 1.36 + 1.15); IV 3.87 (1.28 + 1.26 + 1.33).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1437,150,393]" pageId="22" pageNumber="309">Leg macrosetae: Femur I d1-1-1, p1di, r0; II d1-1-1, p1di, r1di; III d1-1-1, p1di, r0 (or r1di); IV d1-1-1, p1di, r0. Patella I–II 0, III–IV p0, r1. Tibia I p0-1-0, r0, v2-2-2; II p0-1-0, r0, v1r-2-2; III p0-1-1-0, r0-1-1-0, v1p-0-0-1p (or v1p-0-0-2); IV p0-1-1-0, r0-1-1-0, v1p-0-0-2. Metatarsus I p1di, r0, v2-0-2; II p1-0-1, r1di, v2-0-2; III d1p-0-0, p1-0-2, r1-0-2, v2-0-2; IV p1-1-2, r1-1-2, v1p-0-2.</paragraph>
